ces remote-sensing and communication technologies may be reconfiguring the practices and scope of global health.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Peckham, Robert", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sinha, Ria", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Digital divide", "Ebola", "Epidemic intelligence", "Satellites", "Vertical geopolitics", "West Africa", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/6a2093cf36935c664f09d7f9a4154d81", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/bb1532f022c592c7f67bc5a7d86216217d680567aa85e7d25e63b5556f56d502", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/DT2RQLF9", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/DT2RQLF9", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/15e802b03ae8f385290123d8b2eb985e!/b253408-255804", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "24-38", "title": "Geoforum", "volume": "80"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/6a2093cf36935c664f09d7f9a4154d81"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:DT2RQLF9"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.geoforum.2017.01.001"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13528124"}}]}}, "title": "Sat